OL,5, The BBC has defended the inclusion of a
OL,6, wellness business in Dragons' Den after
OL,7, complaints from health groups.         
OL,9,FCampaigners for myalgic                
OL,10,Fencephalomyelitis (ME) complained the  
OL,11,Fshow promoted "unfounded" claims that a
OL,12,Fproduct could help the condition.      
OL,14,FBusinesswoman Giselle Boxer said her   
OL,15,FAcu Seeds product helped aid her       
OL,16,Frecovery from ME.                      
OL,18,FThe BBC said products being featured on
OL,19,Fthe programme should not be seen as an 
OL,20,Fendorsement of them.                   
